# 17. REAL-LIFE ADMIN WORKFLOWS TO REFLECT IN UI

Design the admin panel to support real workflows such as:

## Workflow 1: Inactive user recovery

If user inactive for 3 days:

* show support flag
* allow admin to trigger comeback notification
* recommend easier planner mode
* assign recovery challenge

## Workflow 2: Low mood support

If repeated low mood logs:

* show risk flag
* suggest gentle outreach
* recommend calm resources
* queue supportive AI sequence

## Workflow 3: Quit-support risk monitoring

If many cravings are logged:

* highlight user
* suggest emergency support flow
* allow admin to assign recovery pack

## Workflow 4: Broken streak recovery

If major streak breaks:

* show comeback candidate
* assign comeback challenge
* trigger supportive dashboard mode

## Workflow 5: Workflow failure monitoring

If AI or reminders fail:

* show failure alert
* allow retry
* display last success and error state

